Photo: SuppliedAfrica Day winners (from left) Sazi Ntombela, Phila Myeni, Nomphumelelo Mabizela and Phindile Mkhize. Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories IN celebration of Africa Day, Expand a Sign staff were encouraged to dress up in their respective cultural attire on Thursday, 25 May and were treated to a custom-made Africa-shaped piece of Tasha s Fantastic Fudge. We celebrated our continent s diversity with some good, hearty signing followed by a fashion show displaying various cultural outfits, said Kirsty Fonzari Expand a Sign Marketing Manager. Colleagues judged the outfits and the best dressed male and female titles were awarded to Sazi Ntombela, Nomphumelelo Mabizela and Phindile Mkhize. The winner of the most creative outfit was Phila Myeni. Well done to everyone who participated in our celebration of Africa Day and congratulations to our winners, said Kirsty. - Supplied.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.